A data scientist uses `SNOWFLAKE.CORTEX.COMPLETE` with a message list to control the model's behavior:

```sql
SELECT SNOWFLAKE.CORTEX.COMPLETE(
  'llama3-70b-instruct',
  [
    {'role': 'system', 'content': 'You are a helpful data analyst. Always respond in JSON format.'},
    {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Summarize this review: ' || review_text}
  ]
) FROM reviews;
```

What does the `{'role': 'system', ...}` message do?
